{"tid":161669,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"m18講場：鄭丹瑞教領展商戶享受壓力","createTime":"2017-03-18T16:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T02:23:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd88db3f229d53ce39d0bfe8f3fb9af42d68bdb","tid":161669,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20160317/photo/bkn-20160317130232562-0317_00842_001_01p.jpg?20160317140910\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20160317%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160317130232562-0317_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20160317140910&h=a08b9195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭丹瑞向商戶分享個人面對逆境時，如何變強。(相片由領展提供)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=c5f8d4b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 從事演藝事業近40年的鄭丹瑞，於領展「商戶學堂」分享其不為人知的影視歷程辛酸史，勉勵及教導一眾領展商戶在面對問題及逆境時應如何克服，而最重要是保持正確的心態，從失敗中學習，發揮正能量。<br />\n鄭丹瑞指，自1978年畢業加入電視台出任編劇，短短1年半已升至編審，但「視途」失意，更考慮過轉行做保險經紀，但抱著「永不放棄」的心態，加上學懂如何借助自己的「商譽」及大眾的「口碑」去宣傳執導的電影，做到起死回生、票房大賣。<br />\n佢話，「無壓力就不會進步，所以要好好享受壓力的來臨」，只要做到「今日比當日更強大」，期待下一個壓力來臨，會令你人生一路向前走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20160317/bkn-20160317130232562-0317_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20160317%2Fbkn-20160317130232562-0317_00842_001.html&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=ca4eb46f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20160317/bkn-20160317130232562-0317_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7650ee1e8b2280050c8d17eb7bf1e4c037b6559c","tid":161669,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big